{
  "stem": "5758.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I stole some cement bags, paper, which carried this-- cement was in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I put on this cement bag underneath my pajamas, striped clothes, on-- onto the body, because-- hoping that this would us-- protect me a little bit against the cold.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was-- I think it was very lucky that I had this, because it did somehow help.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we walked [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remember we stopped in a cegla factory, in-- in a brick factory in Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I think it was Gleiwitz, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one surrounded by SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "One of the-- from our group tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "SS shot him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We continued walking and walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I believe we walked somewhere around 80 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was freezing cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We want-- went on the road, tree-- trees and woods on either side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Absolutely nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We picked up snow, put the snow into our mouths to get some liquid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And people collapsed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Soon--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I weakened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you don't-- I don't think except-- The thought was that I wanted to survive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw them shooting people who collapsed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to make sure that I don't collapse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to walk this amount with wooden shoes, wooden soles, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] your feet were blood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Must be blood, because I felt some liquid in there from walking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had here, on both arms, you know, eczemas, or-- don't know-- which never healed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, I had it for even months, months afterwards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just doesn't-- didn't heal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we walked, and people, one-- a few, run into the woods, thought-- thought to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But again, SS shot them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when people collapsed, they were shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was will in me.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
